targets.query: SELECT "avg"/1000 FROM "autogen"."jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /$application/ AND "statut" = 'ok' AND "transaction" =~ /^$script_name.*$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "transaction"

SELECT sum("count") FROM "autogen"."jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /$application/ AND "statut" = 'ko' AND "transaction" =~ /^$script_name.*$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1m), "transaction" fill(null)
SELECT sum("count") as "summary" FROM  "autogen"."jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /$application/ AND "statut" = 'all' AND "transaction" =~ /^UC\d{2}.*/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "transaction"
SELECT sum("count") as "passed" FROM  "autogen"."jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /$application/ AND "statut" = 'ok' AND "transaction" =~ /^UC\d{2}.*/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "transaction"
SELECT sum("count") as "failed" FROM "autogen"."jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /$application/ AND "statut" = 'ko' AND "transaction" =~ /^UC\d{2}.*/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "transaction"
SELECT (min("min")+1)/1000 as "min" FROM "autogen"."jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /$application/ AND "statut" = 'ok' AND "transaction" =~ /^UC\d{2}.*/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "transaction"
SELECT max("max")/1000 as "max" FROM "autogen"."jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /$application/ AND "statut" = 'ok' AND "transaction" =~ /^UC\d{2}.*/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "transaction"
SELECT median("avg")/1000 as "median" FROM "autogen"."jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /$application/ AND "statut" = 'ok' AND "transaction" =~ /^UC\d{2}.*/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "transaction"
SELECT last("avg")/1000 as "avg" FROM "autogen"."jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /$application/ AND "statut" = 'ok' AND "transaction" =~ /^UC\d{2}.*/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "transaction"

SELECT last("pct90.0")/1000 as "percentile 90" FROM "autogen"."jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /$application/ AND "statut" = 'ok' AND "transaction" =~ /^UC\d{2}.*/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "transaction"

SELECT sum("count") AS "errors summary" FROM "autogen"."jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /$application/ AND "responseCode" != '0' AND "responseCode" != '') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "responseCode", "responseMessage", "transaction", "application"
SELECT sum("count") AS "all" FROM "autogen"."jmeter" WHERE ("transaction" =~ /UC/ AND "application" =~ /$application/ AND  "statut" = 'all') AND $timeFilter
SELECT sum("count") as "error" FROM "autogen"."jmeter" WHERE ("transaction" =~ /UC/ AND "statut" = 'ok' AND "application" =~ /$application/) AND $timeFilter
SELECT sum("count") as "error" FROM "autogen"."jmeter" WHERE ("transaction" =~ /UC/ AND "statut" = 'ko' AND "application" =~ /$application/) AND $timeFilter
SELECT last("maxAT") FROM "autogen"."jmeter" WHERE ("transaction" = 'internal' AND "application" =~ /$application/) AND $timeFilter Group By "application"
SELECT sum("count") FROM "autogen"."jmeter" WHERE ("transaction" =~ /^UC$all_script_names.*$/ AND "application" =~ /$application/ AND "statut" = 'ko') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "application"
SELECT sum("count") FROM "autogen"."jmeter" WHERE ("transaction" =~ /UC/ AND "application" =~ /$application/ AND "statut" = 'ok') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1m)
SELECT sum("count") FROM "jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /$application/ AND "statut" = 'ko' AND "transaction" =~ /UC/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1m)

SELECT sum("threads_per_script") FROM (SELECT last("maxAT") AS "threads_per_script" FROM "autogen"."jmeter" WHERE ("transaction" = 'internal' AND "application" =~ /$application/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "application", time($Time)) GROUP BY time($Time)
SELECT mean("count")/5 FROM "autogen"."jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /$application/ AND "transaction" =~ /^UC\d{2}.*/ AND "statut" = 'ok' ) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1m) fill(null)
SELECT last("maxAT") FROM "autogen"."jmeter" WHERE ("transaction" = 'internal' AND "application" =~ /^$application.*$node_name$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($Time), "application" fill(null)
